repos.name: Brawdle
repos.description: Brawdle is an engaging guess game based on Brawl Stars 🎮, where players use data about champions to make educated guesses. Dive into the world of Brawl Stars characters and challenge your knowledge by guessing champions from provided data. 🌟🔍 Test your skills and see how well you know your favorite Brawl Stars heroes! 🌟

repos.name: CPU
repos.description: Explore the 🖥️ CPU diagram 📊 and assembler 🛠️ written in Python, designed to provide a comprehensive understanding of CPU architecture and assembly language programming. This project offers visual insights into CPU components and their interactions, complemented by an assembler capable of translating assembly code into machine code instructions.

repos.name: Data
repos.description: CPP-Data is a 💪 robust C++ library for streamlined data handling. It offers versatile tools and utilities for managing diverse data structures and operations, perfect for projects of any scale. Whether 📦 storing, retrieving 🔄 vectors or arrays, CPP-Data simplifies is. It also provides the flexibility to hash data using custom functions 🔒✨

repos.name: JS-Cookies
repos.description: 🍪JS Cookies is a simple JavaScript library 📕 for managing browser cookies. You can easily set 🎫 cookies, retrieve 🎁 cookie values, and remove 🧨 cookies. The library is lightweight and ideal for handle cookies in web app by javascript.

repos.name: linkfree-generator
repos.description: A simple, free, open-source, and self-hosted alternative to linktree

repos.name: Neural-Network
repos.description: Neural-Network 🧠 is an incredibly versatile and user-friendly library crafted specifically for effortlessly constructing and training neural networks. Whether you're diving into deep learning for the first time or honing your skills, this library provides a robust foundation. 🚀 Built with educational purposes in mind.

repos.name: skill-icons-v2
repos.description: Successor of Skill Icons. Showcase your skills on your Github readme or resumé with ease ✨

repos.name: UwUsiometr
repos.description: Welcome to UwUsiometer 🌸, the ultimate destination to measure your cuteness! 💖 Ever wondered how adorable you really are? Now you can find out with just a snap of a photo 📸.
